  imageAlt={'window-film-philadelphia-uv-blocking-sunlight'}
  flip={true}
  altBg={true}
/>

  <BackAndForthSection
  heading={'UV Blocking Window Film vs. Other Solutions'}
  body={'The sun’s UV rays are one of the leading causes of interior fading and material breakdown. Furniture, carpets, hardwood flooring, and artwork are all vulnerable to sun damage. UV blocking window film in Philadelphia acts like an invisible shield, filtering out harmful rays while still letting natural light into your space. For homeowners, this means protecting your investment and extending the life of your décor. For businesses, it means lower maintenance costs, a more comfortable environment for employees, and an improved customer experience.'}
